{"about_the_game":"Your hometown has suffered catastrophic damage in the wake of a violent storm. Many essential services are out of commission and even the bay entrance has been blocked. It is up to you, our local hero, to come to the aid of the people and rebuild the town's infrastructure. How will you do it? Well, by fishing of course.<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cast your Line</h2></strong><br>Find &amp; catch over 50 different species of fish, each with their own habitat &amp; behaviours. Use bait &amp; place lobster pots to find even more species. Explore multiple biomes around your home as you fill out your fishipedia.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428060/extras/Catch.png?t=1705398713\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Repair your home</h2></strong><br>With the profits from your catch, rebuild the town &amp; restore life into it. As shops &amp; services re-open, you\u2019ll be able to upgrade &amp; customise your boat &amp; gear, allowing you to bring in even more lucrative catches.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428060/extras/Repair.png?t=1705398713\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Race your heart out</h2></strong><br>It's not just about how many fish you can catch. Some sailors like to test their skills in races around the bay. Are you brave enough to compete and collect the spoils?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428060/extras/Race.png?t=1705398713\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Clean up the Sea</h2></strong><br>The aftermath of the storm has filled the sea with debris. Collect any salvage you can find &amp; bring it back to port. You never know what rewards you will get for doing so.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428060/extras/Salvage.png?t=1705398713\" />